chunk_content: Function calling support### Supported modelsThe models page contains the most up-to-date information on regions/models where Assistants are supported.To use all features of function calling including parallel functions, you need to use a model that was released after November 6th 2023.### API Versions- `2024-02-15-preview`- `2024-05-01-preview`
